sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Mouse
participant Cheese
participant Timer
participant MovementRules

Mouse->>Cheese: pickUp()
Cheese-->>Mouse: grantPowerMode()
Mouse->>Timer: start(turns = 3)

note over Mouse,Timer: While Timer active, Mouse gets 2-step movement per Mouse Turn

loop Each Mouse Turn while Timer active
  Mouse->>MovementRules: getStepBudget(powerMode=true) = 2
  Mouse->>Timer: decrementTurn()
  alt Timer expired after decrement
    Timer-->>Mouse: expired
    Mouse-->>Mouse: exitPowerMode()
  else still active
    Timer-->>Mouse: remaining > 0
  end
end